						</v8:item>
						<v8:item>
							<v8:lang>en</v8:lang>
							<v8:content>The organizations and individual entrepreneurs using the simplified system of taxation, and the main economic activity specified in paragraph 8 of Part 1 of Article 58 of the Federal Law № 212-FZ</v8:content>
